WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.240 --> 00:00:02.427
Hey, good morning family.

00:00:02.427 --> 00:00:03.863
Praise the Lord.

00:00:03.863 --> 00:00:05.920
Thank you for joining me today.

00:00:05.920 --> 00:00:08.240
Well, I have my sweetheart with me today, Diana.

00:00:08.240 --> 00:00:09.519
She's behind the camera.

00:00:09.519 --> 00:00:11.079
She's going to pray with us.

00:00:11.079 --> 00:00:11.339
Hi.

00:00:11.339 --> 00:00:15.600
I appreciate so many of you all praying with us last time.

00:00:15.600 --> 00:00:16.679
That was heavy.

00:00:16.679 --> 00:00:21.600
And there was a very heavy atmosphere because of what I was seeing.

00:00:21.600 --> 00:00:22.950
I don't carry it, folks.

00:00:22.950 --> 00:00:26.880
The moment this prayer session is over, I cast my care.

00:00:26.880 --> 00:00:32.380
Folks, I've been doing this for what is it now, 30 years plus, I've been praying like this.

00:00:32.380 --> 00:00:34.479
I want you to know it's grown.

00:00:34.479 --> 00:00:36.160
I have to say that it's grown.

00:00:36.160 --> 00:00:39.760
But when I see like that, people go, 'How do you carry all that?

00:00:39.760 --> 00:00:40.048
What do you do?

00:00:40.480 --> 00:00:40.960
Oh, Brandon, poor Brandon.

00:00:41.440 --> 00:00:42.213
Oh my goodness.

00:00:42.213 --> 00:00:43.973
' I put it on a shelf.

00:00:43.973 --> 00:00:45.359
It's not my problem.

00:00:45.359 --> 00:00:46.960
It's not my problem.

00:00:46.960 --> 00:00:49.751
I don't let it on the inside of me.

00:00:49.751 --> 00:00:54.432
The visions and the things that I see, I don't let them on the inside of me.

00:00:54.432 --> 00:00:59.200
I give it and then I lay it up there and I go, 'It's not affecting me.

00:00:59.200 --> 00:01:01.120
I'm not living that.

00:01:01.120 --> 00:01:08.139
I'm just a vessel that He uses, an instrument that He prays through to get the job done.

00:01:08.139 --> 00:01:13.120
' But I refuse to live in that vision.

00:01:13.120 --> 00:01:15.280
I'm always in the right place.

00:01:15.280 --> 00:01:19.620
I'm going to say this—I always say this—I'm always in the right place at the right time.

00:01:19.620 --> 00:01:23.360
I'm always doing what He tells me to do at all times.

00:01:23.360 --> 00:01:29.662
And I'm going to hear Him at all times, and I'm going to see everything He needs me to see at all times.

00:01:29.662 --> 00:01:31.050
I won't miss it.

00:01:31.050 --> 00:01:33.555
I'm going to listen to my Father.

00:01:33.555 --> 00:01:37.360
And even if I do, I pick myself up and I say, 'Hey, you know what?

00:01:37.360 --> 00:01:39.248
I got a skinned knee, but I'm going to keep going.

00:01:39.248 --> 00:01:43.848
' You don't camp around failure.

00:01:43.848 --> 00:01:47.933
You don't camp around success.

00:01:47.933 --> 00:01:49.646
I stay vertical.

00:01:49.646 --> 00:02:03.306
Because if you look at your failures or you look at your successes, failures get you to have no confidence at all and you don't want to keep going, and successes give you a big head and you go, 'Well, it's all about me.

00:02:03.306 --> 00:02:03.644
' No, no, no, no.

00:02:03.982 --> 00:02:05.180
It's all about Him.

00:02:05.180 --> 00:02:14.560
And if you stay vertical and you're always looking at Him, regardless if it's a success or a failure, it's all about Him.

00:02:14.560 --> 00:02:20.640
I don't let my eyes get all—it's like, 'Oh, the star-struckness of things.

00:02:20.640 --> 00:02:21.720
' Who cares?

00:02:21.720 --> 00:02:22.800
Keep moving.

00:02:22.800 --> 00:02:26.688
A success is a success, but guess what?

00:02:26.688 --> 00:02:30.999
It's yesterday's news after a while.

00:02:30.999 --> 00:02:32.559
Does that make sense?

00:02:32.559 --> 00:02:33.039
A failure is a failure.

00:02:33.760 --> 00:02:41.860
People will camp around your failures a lot because they are insecure about their own lives and their own abilities and what God's doing with them.

00:02:41.860 --> 00:02:45.150
So they want to bring you down and make you camp around your failures.

00:02:45.150 --> 00:02:46.440
They like it.

00:02:46.440 --> 00:02:49.030
So I always say, you know what?

00:02:49.030 --> 00:02:51.920
Most people don't want to see you successful.

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:55.440
Most people don't want to see you have a big ministry.

00:02:55.440 --> 00:02:58.539
Most people don't want to see you have a big following or money or anything.

00:02:58.539 --> 00:03:02.453
They just want you to stay a little lower than them.

00:03:02.453 --> 00:03:04.120
A little lower than them.

00:03:04.120 --> 00:03:07.920
And so I just want to say that it's the truth.

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:09.656
But I'm going to tell you, we don't camp there.

00:03:09.656 --> 00:03:10.304
So what do we do?

00:03:10.304 --> 00:03:14.468
We keep our eyes on Jesus, for we know what is coming.

00:03:14.468 --> 00:03:19.506
We know what's coming, and what's coming: a shaking to awaken.

00:03:19.506 --> 00:03:21.154
A shaking to awaken.

00:03:21.485 --> 00:03:25.420
I'm not worried about the shaking to awaken in that moment.

00:03:25.420 --> 00:03:31.040
I'm going to tell you yesterday when you all prayed with me, that was heavy.

00:03:31.040 --> 00:03:31.480
It was heavy.

00:03:32.170 --> 00:03:32.420
Why?

00:03:32.420 --> 00:03:34.169
Because I saw a lot of destruction.

00:03:34.169 --> 00:03:35.661
I saw a lot of death.

00:03:35.661 --> 00:03:36.779
I saw the earthquakes.

00:03:36.779 --> 00:03:40.553
I saw things on the New Madrid.

00:03:40.553 --> 00:03:44.897
I saw the asteroid again.

00:03:44.897 --> 00:03:57.280
Do you remember I told you I saw a major asteroid that was so big hit outside of the Atlantic Ocean, and it struck down by San Juan, Puerto Rico?

00:03:57.280 --> 00:04:04.480
And it was so massive that it created a tsunami wave that covered the islands.

00:04:04.480 --> 00:04:07.326
It went clear into Miami.

00:04:07.326 --> 00:04:10.628
It went clear into Cape Hatteras.

00:04:10.628 --> 00:04:11.793
All those islands.

00:04:11.793 --> 00:04:15.159
It was such a major tsunami wave.

00:04:15.159 --> 00:04:27.592
It was like 200 stories high—like a huge wave, two huge waves that came in and washed way inland, caused great destruction.

00:04:27.592 --> 00:04:32.479
And many people were sucked out to sea.

00:04:32.479 --> 00:04:35.371
I told you I saw a laser.

00:04:35.903 --> 00:04:39.004
The United States has lasers now.

00:04:39.004 --> 00:04:42.068
I don't know if this is top-secret information, so whatever.

00:04:42.068 --> 00:04:45.466
I do my best, but I saw lasers.

00:04:45.466 --> 00:05:01.071
And it was a green laser, a green-looking laser that hit this rock because missiles were not able to move fast enough to shoot it out of the sky.

00:05:01.071 --> 00:05:10.535
So any kind of military missile that was like, you know, like President Trump's wanting to create this new golden dome, the missiles weren't fast enough.

00:05:10.535 --> 00:05:21.550
So it was created—I saw lasers on all kinds of parts of the United States that were like a defense.

00:05:21.550 --> 00:05:32.897
So, this laser that is around the New Orleans area, God help me, I saw this laser come out of the sky.

00:05:32.897 --> 00:05:42.510
And when this asteroid was traveling from west to east, it was moving so fast that there was nothing else that could hit it.

00:05:42.510 --> 00:05:50.091
And a laser from the New Orleans area hit this thing in half.

00:05:50.091 --> 00:05:59.360
And when it did, it disintegrated parts of it, and particles fell down and caused havoc.

00:05:59.360 --> 00:06:05.608
But the major big part of it fell in the Atlantic Ocean out by San Juan, Puerto Rico.

00:06:05.608 --> 00:06:09.510
And it was so big that it caused all these waves.

00:06:09.720 --> 00:06:11.280
The waves went clear into Africa.

00:06:11.280 --> 00:06:13.213
They went clear into England.

00:06:13.213 --> 00:06:19.120
It was a massive worldwide event that caused major destruction.

00:06:19.120 --> 00:06:21.307
So this is part of the things I see again.

00:06:21.307 --> 00:06:22.860
I saw the sun.

00:06:22.860 --> 00:06:25.216
I told you I saw the sun.

00:06:25.216 --> 00:06:28.524
I said, 'I see the time of day again, Braden.

00:06:28.524 --> 00:06:31.355
' I see the time of day again.

00:06:31.355 --> 00:06:39.234
The sun is about in the summer because there were leaves on the trees, and I could see the Mississippi Valley.

00:06:39.234 --> 00:06:54.469
I could see the sun was going down in the west, but it was right at about a position where the sun was shining upon the trees.

00:06:57.940 --> 00:07:01.531
I saw the barges going down again.

00:07:02.822 --> 00:07:12.069
And what was interesting was the asteroid vision went and coincided with the EMP vision because it was all happening so fast.

00:07:15.987 --> 00:07:26.384
I saw Asian men on a barge coming down the Mississippi, going up and down the Mississippi River, harvesting oats, harvesting grains.

00:07:26.384 --> 00:07:31.129
And they were taking these grains and these oats back to Asia.

00:07:32.029 --> 00:07:50.060
But on this, they had a platform that opened up, and there was a black and white missile that came up out of the belly of this barge that had 'USSR' written on the side of the missile.

00:07:50.060 --> 00:08:06.430
And when they did, they got out to the Gulf of America and they put this barge in the middle of the Gulf and they shot that rocket out over the mainland of America.

00:08:06.430 --> 00:08:09.110
And when it did, it exploded.

00:08:09.110 --> 00:08:12.640
And they said, 'It's not going to go high enough.

00:08:12.640 --> 00:08:15.675
It's not getting enough altitude going up.

00:08:15.675 --> 00:08:36.800
' And when it did, it popped and it went over Kentucky, Tennessee, parts of Alabama, Mississippi, Georgia, the panhandle of Florida, Pennsylvania, Virginia, over that area.

00:08:36.800 --> 00:08:42.480
It did not get far enough to the border of Arkansas and Oklahoma.

00:08:42.480 --> 00:08:46.811
But the further it went out, because it didn't get high enough, right?

00:08:46.811 --> 00:08:48.400
That's what I'm trying to tell you all.

00:08:48.400 --> 00:08:52.675
And I'm trying to make this as quick as possible so I don't waste your time.

00:08:53.070 --> 00:09:02.444
It went up and it popped, but there was still on the West Coast cell phones, electricity, and things like that.

00:09:02.444 --> 00:09:07.230
It was just about the East Coast.

00:09:07.240 --> 00:09:07.669
Okay.

00:09:07.669 --> 00:09:18.600
So, there was still power, but there was no cell phones or internet in Oklahoma.

00:09:18.600 --> 00:09:24.120
So, this was a very serious vision that I had.

00:09:24.120 --> 00:09:26.800
And so, the Lord brought it up again.

00:09:26.800 --> 00:09:30.139
And He showed this to me again last time.

00:09:30.139 --> 00:09:32.382
There were so many events I saw.

00:09:32.382 --> 00:09:45.263
And this is what I thought was interesting: every major catastrophic event that I have seen came up before me again in that last one.

00:09:45.263 --> 00:09:53.025
In that last one, I saw it on timestamps: Earthquakes and Tsunamis Prophecy.

00:09:56.730 --> 00:09:57.180
And I saw earthquakes.

00:10:06.920 --> 00:10:07.480
I saw major tsunamis in Japan again.

00:10:09.480 --> 00:10:15.360
And it was like it was all like a movie screen of everything that I've ever seen, all happening all at once.

00:10:15.360 --> 00:10:15.749
Why?

00:10:34.840 --> 00:10:35.250
I don't know.

00:10:35.250 --> 00:10:42.143
Like I said, and whenever you're seeing all that at once, it was so heavy I went quiet.

00:10:47.320 --> 00:10:47.940
So that's what I'm trying to explain to you what happened last time so that you know.

00:10:47.940 --> 00:10:48.560
Okay.

00:10:48.560 --> 00:10:52.620
So it is what it is.

00:10:52.620 --> 00:10:55.560
So there.

00:10:55.560 --> 00:11:01.080
So, now we're going to go to the journey on Trump's social media, Truth Social.

00:11:01.080 --> 00:11:08.800
He sold 50 shares, from what I understand, to 50 different companies, and they bought into it.

00:11:08.800 --> 00:11:12.275
Bought into it, I guess, is how I'm seeing it.

00:11:12.275 --> 00:11:15.589
Please don't butcher me, but I'm just saying they bought into it, right?

00:11:16.366 --> 00:11:18.940
So when they did this, he raised $2.

00:11:18.940 --> 00:11:22.480
5 billion to buy Bitcoin at an all-time high.

00:11:22.480 --> 00:11:24.499
Usually people buy low and sell high.

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:35.055
I just thought that was interesting.

00:11:35.055 --> 00:11:55.793
I don't know if he's purchased the shares of Bitcoin yet, but he's saying he's going to or he's already done it.

00:11:55.793 --> 00:12:02.857
Maybe that's what made it go to an all-time high, but now it's crashing back down.

00:12:12.427 --> 00:12:12.684
It goes back up, it goes down, it goes up and everything.

00:12:12.684 --> 00:12:18.199
So it's incredible, isn't it?

00:12:18.199 --> 00:12:33.230
So, we just see the whole change of all the things of this new industrial revolution, all of it happening all at once.

00:12:33.240 --> 00:12:34.860
It's all changing.

00:12:34.860 --> 00:12:36.075
Everything's changing.

00:12:36.075 --> 00:12:43.000
So, when we get to this time next year, what does that look like?

00:12:57.906 --> 00:12:58.280
I saw everything will change.

00:12:58.280 --> 00:13:04.520
Life as you know it will change in a 24-hour period with an event that's coming.

00:13:04.520 --> 00:13:19.155
With an event that's coming, everything that we see, everything that we know—just how some events have changed things in the past with Homeland Security and things like that—there'll be things coming in the days ahead that will change everything in a 24-hour period.

00:13:19.155 --> 00:13:24.040
And life as you know it will not ever be the same.

00:13:27.200 --> 00:13:27.413
I saw gardens again.

00:13:39.080 --> 00:13:39.260
I saw people growing gardens in their backyards trying to get food because there was no food.

00:13:49.540 --> 00:13:49.955
And I kept hearing the Father say, 'There's a great humbling, for they have stuck their nose up to the sky at me.

00:14:15.091 --> 00:14:15.486
They have got a stiff neck of pride towards me.

00:14:19.244 --> 00:14:20.054
And there is a great day of humbling.

00:14:20.054 --> 00:14:22.599
There are days of humbling coming.

00:14:25.516 --> 00:14:25.787
And I just tell you this to warn you.

00:14:25.787 --> 00:14:33.220
' And he said, 'The remnant, the church that is awake, will hear what's about to take place.

00:14:33.220 --> 00:14:35.714
' And most of you are hearing it.

00:14:35.714 --> 00:14:40.810
If you're on this channel, I'm warning you now.

00:14:42.456 --> 00:14:43.659
And so you prepare your house.

00:14:53.880 --> 00:14:54.273
You prepare you.

00:14:54.273 --> 00:14:56.240
You prepare your mind.

00:15:09.320 --> 00:15:09.520
Be prepared, for the harvest is plentiful and the laborers are few, and he is the Lord of the harvest.

00:15:09.520 --> 00:15:16.040
Many things that you will see in the days ahead, it's because it's one last call.

00:15:16.040 --> 00:15:24.199
Like I said, you see all the AI, you see all this stuff.

00:15:24.199 --> 00:15:25.821
It's just exciting.

00:15:25.821 --> 00:15:29.474
Don't you think that the end is coming so quick?

00:15:29.474 --> 00:15:31.449
People are upset about it.

00:15:31.449 --> 00:15:38.666
God told me today, he said, 'Brandon, I don't want you focusing on my coming.

00:15:55.253 --> 00:15:55.679
I want you to focus on the task at hand: bring in my harvest.

00:15:55.679 --> 00:16:00.899
Do not get lost in the rapture and parking yourself there.

00:16:00.899 --> 00:16:05.380
Don't get lost in parking yourself around, 'Well, we're heavenbound.

00:16:05.380 --> 00:16:14.092
' Focus on the war at hand: bringing in the lost and the unsaved to Jesus Christ by the millions.

00:16:14.092 --> 00:16:18.703
That's what we should be focusing on right now.

00:16:18.703 --> 00:16:25.817
There are many people that if they die today, they will not make it.

00:16:25.817 --> 00:16:29.310
And those are the ones that he's after.

00:16:29.310 --> 00:16:32.587
He's leaving the ninety-nine to go after the one.

00:16:32.587 --> 00:16:36.516
But he's using you and me to do it.

00:16:48.688 --> 00:16:49.297
And it's going to take finances.

00:16:49.297 --> 00:16:53.560
So, we need to believe big.

00:16:56.880 --> 00:17:02.815
And that's why I'm trying to tell you to get that inward image of the blessing on the inside of you.

00:17:02.815 --> 00:17:04.667
Imagine yourself having it.

00:17:04.667 --> 00:17:06.910
Imagine yourself living it and program your mind.

00:17:06.910 --> 00:17:09.227
It's like he told Diana and me today.

00:17:09.227 --> 00:17:14.600
He said, 'You've had too much poverty on the inside of you.

00:17:14.600 --> 00:17:18.930
You have thought too much poverty because you were raised that way.

00:17:18.930 --> 00:17:24.400
You've got to change and train your thoughts by renewing your mind on this beautiful Bible more.

00:17:24.400 --> 00:17:26.800
' He corrected me.

00:17:26.800 --> 00:17:29.771
He said, 'You need to be in that book more.

00:17:29.771 --> 00:17:45.140
You need to be in that Bible more, renewing your mind to what my word says about you instead of that poverty mentality of not enough, always afraid of not having your bills met.

00:17:45.140 --> 00:17:57.236
' I want you to get—when you get that inward image of the covenant of what God has done for you, of realizing that everything in your life has an expiration date.

00:17:57.236 --> 00:17:59.200
Everything in your life has an expiration date.

00:17:59.200 --> 00:18:01.919
No matter the sickness, if you've had it, picture yourself healed.

00:18:01.919 --> 00:18:03.250
Picture yourself walking in divine health.

00:18:03.250 --> 00:18:07.1000
Get an inner image of 'I am healed by the stripes of Jesus.

00:18:07.1000 --> 00:18:15.424
' I get the picture of Megan coming in and sitting right here beside me and telling you that he has healed her.

00:18:15.424 --> 00:18:21.820
You have to visualize it inside because that's what I see, and I grab ahold of it by faith.

00:18:21.820 --> 00:18:29.250
But if you see yourself always broke, always sick, always defeated, always, then you're going to walk that way.

00:18:46.559 --> 00:18:46.932
But I start training myself to think like this Bible tells me I can have it.

00:18:46.932 --> 00:18:53.263
I can do what this Bible tells me I can do.

00:18:53.263 --> 00:18:56.171
By his stripes, I am healed.

00:18:56.171 --> 00:18:57.440
What does that look like?

00:18:57.440 --> 00:18:59.236
Does it look like Megan is right now?

00:19:08.088 --> 00:19:08.471
No.

00:19:25.220 --> 00:19:25.670
So, I refuse to keep seeing her that way.

00:19:25.670 --> 00:19:32.360
I see her healed, and I see Diana and me blessed.

00:19:32.360 --> 00:19:38.057
Do I see us always doing eBay and Poshmark all the time?

00:19:38.057 --> 00:19:38.720
No.

00:19:38.720 --> 00:19:40.960
There's an expiration date to that.

00:19:40.960 --> 00:19:46.260
I believe full-time ministry without having to think about Poshmark or eBay is coming.

00:19:46.260 --> 00:19:49.880
Does that make sense, what I'm trying to tell you all?

00:19:49.880 --> 00:19:52.720
There is a level of blessing.

00:19:52.720 --> 00:19:54.148
There is a level of ministry.

00:19:54.148 --> 00:19:55.880
I get an inner image of this.

00:19:56.960 --> 00:19:58.057
And that's what happens every year with Megan.

00:19:58.057 --> 00:20:07.989
Every year, I'm saying by my birthday next year, Megan is going to be completely healed by this time.

00:20:07.989 --> 00:20:09.543
I believe it.

00:20:13.070 --> 00:20:13.385
And I have these milestones.

00:20:13.385 --> 00:20:17.085
On July 3rd is my birthday; July 3rd, I'll be 45.

00:20:17.370 --> 00:20:23.056
And I always told Diana by 40 years old, I'm going to be in full-time ministry.

00:20:23.056 --> 00:20:31.280
Well, it didn't happen like I thought, but I'm 45, and I basically am in full-time ministry.

00:20:31.280 --> 00:20:48.503
Basically, I don't have a big ministry like, you know, some people have, but I have a YouTube ministry, and I have an inward image of what God had told me I'm going to do.

00:20:48.503 --> 00:20:50.879
And I'm 45 this year.

00:20:50.879 --> 00:21:01.280
And I said, 'Five years, I've been quoting, and I even told my family, I said, 'I will be where I'm supposed to be before I'm 50.

00:21:01.280 --> 00:21:07.530
' I refuse to go by 50 and say, 'Well, I never got where God called me to be.

00:21:07.530 --> 00:21:17.466
' I believe that God's called me to do what he's called me to do, and I got an inward image of that by 45.

00:21:17.466 --> 00:21:31.720
This is my 45th birthday on July 3rd, and I told Diana, I said, 'We're going to believe this, and look, folks, it's just changing your negative, stinking thinking is what I'm trying to tell you.

00:21:31.720 --> 00:21:39.359
Changing it and seeing yourself being successful and saying, 'God, I know what your word says about me.

00:21:39.359 --> 00:21:46.560
I know what your word says about me, but I see myself doing it because I'm just so done with that me-mouth victim mentality.

00:21:46.560 --> 00:21:53.387
' And I'm telling you, I played the victim a lot in my life.

00:21:53.387 --> 00:21:56.937
'Woe is me, I've had all this.

00:22:17.020 --> 00:22:17.587
I was a janitor for all these years, and I haven't been real smart and had a real good education.

00:22:17.587 --> 00:22:23.985
' And I thought, 'You know what?

00:22:32.040 --> 00:22:32.320
